{"tid":858690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿同居女友掛住湊仔 「呷醋男」虐打2稚兒被捕","createTime":"2018-10-12T03:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T09:24:04.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4a46a2aa5949a4eb9696fd924017d93c4af450a0","tid":858690,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:44:19.000Z","msg":"「呷醋男」涉虐打同居女友2幼子被捕。現場深水埗南昌街153-155號一單位，一名男子疑因24歲姓雷同居女友，只顧照料2名與前夫所生的3歲及5歲幼子，將他冷待，大感不滿。至今日(12日)凌晨1時許，2人為此事起爭執，期間一對稚子竟成「出氣袋」，遭人出手毆打，2童母親上前制止，並致電社工求助。稍後，一對男女社工趕抵現場，雷女致電報警。<br />\n<br />\n警員到場調查，遇襲2稚童分別眼、耳、額頭及面腫，由女社工及手背有紋身母親抱上救護車，送院治理。警員經調查後，將涉嫌傷人的32歲姓劉男子拘捕。案件列普通襲擊及襲擊致造成實際身體傷害，交由深水埗警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pnRvHvdbNkpCIo6dtHLY.g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/60f6d31a6bba003074becf3e20ec4295\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpnRvHvdbNkpCIo6dtHLY.g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F60f6d31a6bba003074becf3e20ec4295&h=cb749373&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc260c5a952dcf08cfcdcc73c33ca56d757c82d1","tid":858690,"uid":63909,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:45:13.000Z","msg":"24歲姓雷同居女友，只顧照料2名與前夫所生的3歲及5歲幼子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89a97dbd5e9c79b058544d19e6b0f368461775b","tid":858690,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f8df01cf6d962f813da40f9f75929208a45c09","tid":858690,"uid":67500,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:49:04.000Z","msg":